subject: Good Day,
body:
Good Day,
I Hope this Mail Finds You Well; Please, I write To Let You Know  If
You Have Received My Previous Message  I Sent You Last Time?
Krystal Hawley From USA
I Await Your Reply.
Warmest Regards,
Krystal Hawley.

subject: Re: Good Day,
body:
Hello Krystal Hawley,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I apologize, but I don't recall receiving any previous messages from you. Could you please remind me what the message was about? I would be happy to assist you if I can.

Best wishes,
Sherman
